New Records: Rilee Rossouw scored 109 runs, the highest by a South African batter in a T20I match; Anrich Nortje took four wickets, his best T20I performance
Key Match Events: Anrich Nortje's four-wicket haul in quick succession was a turning point
Post-Match Reflections: Rilee Rossouw was named Player of the Match; the win boosted South Africa's net run rate
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was held at the Sydney Cricket Ground; the win put South Africa at the top of Group 2
